<section xml:id="section-sys-diff-eq-terminology">

<title>Terminology and notation</title>

<p><dl width="narrow">

	<li>
	<title>system of differential equations</title>
	<idx><h>system</h><h>of differential equations</h></idx>
	<p>
	a collection of (usually linear) differential equations in the unknown functions <m>y_1(t), y_2(t), \dotsc, y_n(t)</m>
	</p>
	</li>

	<li>
	<title>coupled system of differential equations</title>
	<idx><h>system</h><h>of differential equations</h></idx>
	<p>
	a system of differential equations where each derivative <m>y_j'(t)</m> is related to a combination of the unknown functions <m>y_1(t), y_2(t), \dotsc, y_n(t)</m>
	</p>
	</li>

</dl></p>

</section>
